How to use? How to connect ?how to paired with "Da fit" app?how to use phone calls? Answer: 1. Please download the "dafit" app and install it, and open the bluetooth on your phone. (Don't connect directly via bluetooth) ------ 2. Open "Dafit" app, click "add a device" to connect --- ---3.Search device "GT88" to connect Note: connect the watch from the app can not use to make calls, you need to follow: Swipe down the watch home page,click "settings" and turn on "phone calls" &" Audio Bluetooth" Why cann't receive notifications on smart watch? Confirm that your social application account is limited to mobile devices only Note:Allow "GT88" to Receive the notifications For iOS:1phone settings> Find the "DaFit" APP> Switch on "Notifications"2.Go to the "DaFit" APP> Device> Click the "Push Notifications"> Switch on all the applications you needFor android:(Go to your phone settings> APPs> Find "Da Fit" APP> Launch settings> Switch on "Run in background")2. (Go to your phone settings> APPs> Find the "DaFit" APP> Switch on "Allow Notifications" and "Permissions")3.Turned on "Push Notifications" on the "Da Fit" APP how to use music player? Select and play your preferred music on either your smartwatch or mobile phone Answer: Locate and tap the "Music Player" icon on your smartwatch. This will open the music player on the smartwatch. (Ensure that the "music player" app on your mobile phone is open and active.) Also, make sure the "Audio Bluetooth" feature is enabled on your smartwatch.On your mobile phone, swipe down on the home page to access the notification panel. Select the smartwatch or mobile phone option to play music. Note: Please be aware that smartwatches do not have built-in storage for music. How to change watch faces and customizable dials? Find more watch faces and customizable watch faces Long-press the watch face page on your smartwatch to choose that you wantFor more watch faces:1.Ensure your smartwatch is paired with the "Dafit" app (not directly connected via Bluetooth).2).Look for the watch faces section within the app.3).Browse through the available watch faces and select the one you preferTo upload your own photos as the watch face:1).Select the "Edit" option within the watch face settings.2).Follow the prompts to customize the watch face using your own photos or images. how to add contacts to smartwatch? how to add contacts to smartwatch? Answer: 1.Please paired with the "dafit" app(Do not connected directly via bluetooth) 2.choose "favorite contacts" to add contacts,(only add to 8 contacts) how to reset? how to reset? Answer: open the "Dafit" app and select "Remove Device".forget the smartwatch(GT88) from your phone's Bluetooth settings.on the smartwatch, go to "Settings" > "System" > "Reset" to perform a factory reset.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice cool watch for kids
reviews.reviewText: My daughter really liked it. Has a lot neat features and is a nice way to be able to track her location as well. Connects to phone and allows calls and messages as well. Good overall smartwatch for the value of the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Muy buen reloj, fácil de usar, me encanta que puedes cambiar las esferas fácilmente con la perilla… y el color muy llamativo y bonitoVery good watch, easy to use, I love that you can easily change the faces with the knob... and the color is very striking and beautiful!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not a bad purchase
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Bought this watch to hold me over until i replace the battery in my Galaxy Smartwatch. So far, i'm pretty happy with my choice of this watch. Pros: Battery lasts an average of 2 1/2 days.Screen is great, it's exactly what is advertised (1.5 in.) and crystal clear. 22mm band is a soft elastic rubber material that is comfortable.Easy to work with integrated apps.Phone call capableStreaming music from phone capable.Cons:Bluetooth overrides phone and plays through watch unless you switch Bluetooth off to phone.Limited watch faces. There is a gallery on "Da fit" app, but it's minimal. Only good thing is the fact that you can add your own background photo.Must have "Da fit" app to use watch features and to connect to phone.All in all, this is a great watch for the price. Noone would ever know you paid 1/10 the price of the flagship devices.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my husband for Xmas and the watch is ok but he wears hearing aids that are controlled through his phone so if we have the audio on on the watch he cannot control his hearing aids, so basically it is just a watch that tracks his steps for him. Also you set a certain face on the watch and all of a sudden the face reverts back to the original face. Wish I had chosen another product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Shinny orange watch that does alot
reviews.reviewText: This is a great watch. Screen is big. Color is bold. Initially I can't get it to charge because I forgot to remove the protection film at the back. It also comes with a protection film on the front and 2 USB charging cable. The phone controls camera shutter, music playback, reads messages, makes and takes phone calls, tracks exercise, tracks sleep, tracks heart rate, blood pressure and blood oxygen levels. It does them all. Perfect for what I need!
